import { Box, Button, CardContent, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export default function login() {
  return (
    <Card sx={{width: 400}}>
        <CardContent>
        
    <Box sx={{
        '& .MuiTextField-root':{
            m:1,
            width: '90%'
        }
    }}>
        
    <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
        <TextField 
        label="Email"
        name="email"
        variant="outlined"/>
        <TextField 
        label="Email"
        name="email"
        variant="outlined"/>
        <Button 
        type = "submit"
        variant="contained"
        size="large"
        sx={{width:'90'}}>Start</Button>
        </form>
        
    </Box>
    </CardContent>
    </Card>
  )
}
